articles.title: Condoms: STI clinics want more people to use them - BBC
articles.description: Clinics say they're seeing more people catching STIs as people opt for other contraceptives.
articles.content:
"So many people hype up the awkwardness of condoms," says sex educator Ruby Rare. "I never think that's more important than sexual health."
